title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 8-2.10 - Wedged doors or gates
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 8-2.10 - Wedged doors or gates

State Regulations

No hoistway door or gate shall be wedged or otherwise
fastened in an open position except as provided in subdivision (f) of section
8-2.18. Notes
